<p> </p>
<ul>
<li>Return flights from the UK to Bergen and back from Ålesund </li>
<li>Scenic transfer from Bergen to Balestrand via 4-hour coastal express boat</li>
<li>Day trip on Flåm railway from Balestrand with packed lunch included</li>
<li>Scenic transfer from Balestrand to Loen via the Gauler mountains</li>
<li>Scenic transfer from Loen to Ålesund via Geiringerfjord ferry and Dalsnibba viewpoint</li>
<li>Accommodation with private facilities throughout</li>
<li>Half board meals included in Balestrand and Loen, plus 1st night in Bergen and Ålesund</li>
<li>Bed &amp; Breakfast for 2nd night in Bergen and Ålesund</li>
<li>Daily packed lunch during your stay in Loen</li>
<li>Guided walks with your Inghams guide in Balestrand, Loen and Ålesund</li>
</ul>
<p>Max group size: 30 people </p>
</div>
